data.value: Full name (will be split into first/last)
KH, TH, VN, ID, MY, PH, MM, LA, SG, BN, CH, JP, KR, IN, PK, BD, LK, NP, BT, MV, OTHER
Must match existing zone in system
Must match existing building in system
ID card or passport photo filename
Column D: DOB - Date of Birth
Column N: IDKH/PASSPORT - ID/Passport photo filename
Column O: WORKINGPERMIT - Work permit photo filename
Column P: VISA - Visa photo filename
1. Fill in data from left to right for best workflow
2. Required fields are in the first 8 columns for easy access
3. Building and Zone names must match exactly with system records
4. ALL photos must be uploaded separately - only include filenames in Excel
5. Document columns (N, O, P) need PHOTO FILENAMES of the documents
6. Photo column (Q) needs PHOTO FILENAME of the worker's portrait
7. Recommended photo naming: id_[name].jpg, wp_[name].jpg, visa_[name].jpg
Nationality: Use codes from Nationality Codes sheet
Sex: M, F, or O only
